"",
"The overview folder has 3 types of files:",
"1. Kinase_summary / kinase enrichment files list kinases.",
"   * Kinase summary: contains summary of their scores (min, max scores), number of sequences, databases.",
"   * _readonly version: just a kinase list for clients.",
"   * Kinase_enrichmetn: a kinase list for the UKA_app.",
"2. KSR (Kinase-Substrate Relationship) summary lists kinase-to-ID data, and summarizes their scores and ranks per db.",
"3. enrichment_<array layouts> lists all IDs and their protein matches. The comment version shows whether the id is high seq sim, low seq sim (not used in uka), or special (e.g. control)",
"Files ending with 'all_filters' have filters: sequence similarity 0.9, Kinase_rank < 13, score >= 300 (no number of sequences filter).",
"Files ending with seqsim0.9 have only sequence similarity filter."
)
